insulte'' || data-sort-value=\"Doueiri\"| [[Ziad Doueiri]] || France, Lebanon\n|-\n| colspan=2| ''[[Lean on Pete]]'' || data-sort-value=\"Haigh\"| [[Andrew Haigh]] || United Kingdom\n|-\n| colspan=2 data-sort-value=\"Leisure\"| ''[[The Leisure Seeker]]'' || data-sort-value=\"Virz\u00ec\"| [[Paolo Virz\u00ec]] || Italy\n|-\n| ''[[Mektoub, My Love: Canto Uno]]'' || ''Mektoub, My Love: Canto Uno'' || data-sort-value=\"Kechiche\"| [[Abdellatif Kechiche]] ||France, Italy\n|-\n| colspan=2| ''[[Mother!]]'' || data-sort-value=\"Aronofsky\"| [[Darren Aronofsky]] ||United States\n|-style=\"background:#FFDEAD;\"\n| colspan=2 data-sort-value=\"Shape\"| ''[[The Shape of Water]]'' || data-sort-value=\"Del Toro\"| [[Guillermo del Toro]] ||United States\n|-\n| colspan=2| ''[[Suburbicon]]'' || data-sort-value=\"Clooney\"| [[George Clooney]] ||United States\n|-\n| colspan=2| ''[[Sweet Country (2017 film)|Sweet Country]]'' || data-sort-value=\"Thornton\"| [[Warwick Thornton]] ||Australia\n|-\n| data-sort-value=\"Third\"| ''[[The Third Murder]]'' || ''Sandome No Satsujin'' ( \u4e09\u5ea6\u76ee\u306e\u6bba\u4eba ) || data-sort-value=\"Hirokazu\"| [[Koreeda Hirokazu]] ||Japan\n|-\n| colspan=2| ''[[Three Billboards Outside Ebbing, Missouri]]'' || data-sort-value=\"McDonagh\"| [[Martin McDonagh]] ||United Kingdom\n|}\n:<span style=\"background:#FFDEAD\">Highlighted title</span> indicates Golden Lion winner.\n\n===Out of Competition===\nThe following films were selected to be screened out of competition:<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.labiennale.org/en/cinema/2017/biennale-cinema-2017-film-fuori-concorso |title=Biennale Cinema 2017, Films out of Competition |work=labiennale.org |accessdate=17 April 2018}}</ref><ref name=\"souls\">{{cite web|url=https://variety.com/2017/film/news/venice-fest-will-honor-jane-fonda-robert-redford-our-souls-at-night-to-world-premiere-1202497297/|title=Venice to Honor Jane Fonda, Robert Redford; Their \u2018Our Souls at Night\u2019 to World Premiere|work=[[Variet