uch]] || France\n|-\n| style=\"background: #ececec; font-size: smaller; text-align: center\" data-sort-value=\"Da\u00efnah\"| N/A || ''[[Da\u00efnah la m\u00e9tisse]]'' (1931) || data-sort-value=\"Gremillon\"| [[Jean Gr\u00e9millon]] || France\n|-\n| ''[[Flavor of Green Tea Over Rice]]'' (1952) || ''Ochazuke No Aji'' || data-sort-value=\"Ozu\"| [[Yasujir\u014d Ozu]] || Japan\n|-\n| colspan=2| ''[[Into the Night (film)|Into the Night]]'' (1985) || data-sort-value=\"Landis\"| [[John Landis]] || United States\n|-\n| colspan=2 data-sort-value=\"Old\"| ''[[The Old Dark House (1932 film)|The Old Dark House]]'' (1932) || data-sort-value=\"Whale\"| [[James Whale]] || United States\n|-\n| ''[[Red Desert (film)|Red Desert]]'' (1964) || data-sort-value=\"Deserto\"| ''Il deserto rosso'' || data-sort-value=\"Antonioni\"| [[Michelangelo Antonioni]] || Italy\n|-\n| colspan=2 data-sort-value=\"Revolt\"| ''[[The Revolt of Mamie Stover (film)|The Revolt of Mamie Stover]]'' (1956) || data-sort-value=\"Walsh\"| [[Raoul Walsh]] || United States\n|-\n| colspan=2| ''[[Rosita (film)|Rosita]]'' (1923) || data-sort-value=\"Lubitsch\"| [[Ernst Lubitsch]] || United States\n|-\n| ''[[Sansho the Bailiff]]'' (1954) || ''Sansh\u014d Day\u016b'' || data-sort-value=\"Mizoguchi\"| [[Kenji Mizoguchi]] || Japan\n|-\n| data-sort-value=\"Story\"| ''[[A Story from Chikamatsu]]'' (1954) || ''Chikamatsu Monogatari'' || data-sort-value=\"Mizoguchi\"| [[Kenji Mizoguchi]] || Japan\n|-\n| data-sort-value=\"Third\"| ''[[The Third Lover]]'' (1962) || data-sort-value=\"Oeil\"| ''L\u2019oeil du malin'' || data-sort-value=\"Chabrol\"| [[Claude Chabrol]] || France\n|-\n| ''[[Two or Three Things I Know About Her]]'' (1967) || ''Deux ou trois choses que je sais d\u2019elle'' || data-sort-value=\"Godard\"| [[Jean-Luc Godard]] || France\n|-\n| ''[[Under the Olive Tree]]'' (1950) || ''Non c\u2019\u00e8 pace tra gli ulivi'' || data-sort-value=\"De Santis\"| [[Giuseppe De Santis]] || Italy\n|-\n| ''Wanderers of the Desert''