hen Nomura Schible]] || United States, Japan\n|-\n| colspan=2| ''[[This is Congo]]'' || data-sort-value=McCabe\"\"| [[Daniel McCabe]] || DR Congo\n|}\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"width:95%; margin-top:2px\"\n|-\n! colspan=4| '''Special events'''\n|-\n! width=\"68%\"| Title\n! width=\"15%\"| Director(s)\n! width=\"17%\"| Production country\n|-\n| ''Casa d\u2019altri'' (16 Min) || [[Gianni Amelio]] || Italy\n|-\n| ''Michael Jackson\u2019s Thriller 3D'' (14 min) || [[John Landis]] || United States\n|-\n| ''Making of Michael Jackson\u2019s Thriller'' (45 min) || Jerry Kramer || United States\n|}\n\n===Horizons===\nThe following films were selected for the Horizons (Orizzonti) section:<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.labiennale.org/en/cinema/2017/biennale-cinema-2017-orizzonti |title=Biennale Cinema 2017 - Orizzonti |work=labiennale.org |accessdate=17 April 2018}}</ref><ref name=\"InComp\"/>\n\n{| class=\"sortable wikitable\" style=\"width:95%; margin-bottom:0px\"\n! colspan=4| Feature films\n|-\n! English title\n! Original title\n! Director(s)\n! Production country\n|-\n| style=\"background: #ececec; font-size: smaller; text-align: center\" data-sort-value=\"Bienheureux\"| N/A || data-sort-value=\"Bienheureux\"| ''[[Les Bienheureux]]'' || data-sort-value=\"Djama\"| [[Sofia Djama]] || France, Belgium\n|-\n| colspan=2| ''[[Caniba (2017 film)|Caniba]]'' || data-sort-value=\"Paravel\"| [[V\u00e9r\u00e9na Paravel]], [[Lucien Castaing-Taylor]] || France\n|-\n| ''[[Cinderella the Cat]]'' || ''Gatta Cenerentola'' || data-sort-value=\"Rak\"| [[Alessandro Rak]], [[Ivan Cappiello]], [[Marino Guarnieri]], [[Dario Sansone]] || Italy\n|-\n| data-sort-value=\"Cousin\"| ''[[The Cousin]]'' || ''Ha Ben Dod'' || data-sort-value=\"Grad\"| [[Tzahi Grad]] || Israel\n|-\n| ''[[Disappearance (2017 Iranian film)|Disappearance]]'' || ''Napadid shodan'' (Irani title) || data-sort-value=\"Asgari\"| [[Ali Asgari (director)|Ali Asgari]] || Iran, Qatar\n|-\n| style=\"background: #ececec; font-size: 