p://outfrontonline.com/culture/film/37th-starz-denver-film-festival-award-winners/|work=Outfront|accessdate=2 June 2015|date=3 December 2014}}</ref>\n| 23 November 2014\n| Best Documentary\n| \n| {{won}}\n|-\n| [[European Film Awards]]<ref>{{cite web |url=https://deadline.com/2015/12/european-film-awards-winners-2015-full-list-1201665776/ |title=European Film Awards Winners 2015: Paolo Sorrentino's 'Youth' Scoops Best Film, Director & Actor For Michael Caine |website=Deadline Hollywood}}</ref>\n| [[28th European Film Awards|12 December 2015]]\n| [[European Film Award for Best Documentary|Best Documentary]]\n| \n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| [[Gotham Awards]] 2015<ref>{{cite web|title=\u2018Spotlight\u2019 Wins Big at 2015 Gotham Awards (FULL LIST)|url=https://variety.com/2015/film/news/gotham-awards-winners-2015-full-list-1201650371/|work=Variety|accessdate=2 December 2015|date=30 November 2015}}</ref>\n| [[Gotham Independent Film Awards 2015|30 November 2015]]\n| Best Documentary\n| \n| {{won}}\n|-\n| [[G\u00f6teborg International Film Festival]] 2015<ref>{{cite web|title=\u2018In Your Arms,\u2019 \u2018Look of Silence\u2019 Top Goteborg Festival|url=https://variety.com/2015/film/news/in-your-arms-look-of-silence-top-goteborg-festival-1201420786/|work=Variety|accessdate=2 February 2015|date=1 February 2015}}</ref>\n| 31 January 2015\n| Dragon Award Best Nordic Documentary\n| \n| {{won}}\n|-\n| rowspan=3| [[London Film Critics' Circle]]<ref>{{cite web|title=\u2018Mad Max: Fury Road,\u2019 \u201945 Years\u2019 Triumph at London Film Critics\u2019 Circle Awards|url=https://variety.com/2016/film/in-contention/mad-max-fury-road-45-years-triumph-at-london-critics-awards-1201681697/|work=Variety|accessdate=18 January 2016|date=17 January 2016}}</ref>\n| rowspan=3| 17 January 2016\n|[[London Film Critics' Circle Award for Film of the Year|Film of the Year]]\n|\n|{{nom}}\n|-\n|Documentary of the Year\n|\n|{{nom}}\n|-\n|[[London Film Critics' Circle Award for Foreign Language Film of the