]]\n*[[Mochhu]]\n*[[Momai Thang]]\n*[[Mongar]]\n*[[Monka]]\n*[[Nab Ch\u00f6te]]\n*[[Naitola]]\n*[[Naktsang]]\n*[[Namtir]]\n*[[Naspe]]\n*[[Ngalangkang]]\n*[[Niche Kalikhola]]\n*[[Nimgong]]\n*[[Ningsang La]]\n*[[Oola, Bhutan|Oola]] (formerly Alla)\n*[[Pachu]]\n*[[Pajo, Bhutan|Pajo]]\n*[[Paro, Bhutan|Paro]]\n*[[Paro Airport]]\n*[[Paten, Bhutan|Paten]]\n*[[Phisugaon]]\n*[[Phuntsholing]]\n*[[Pieksao]]\n*[[Pimi]]\n*[[Pinsoperi]]\n*[[Punakha]]\n*[[Rading]]\n*[[Raga, Bhutan|Raga]]\n*[[Rapley]]\n*[[Rife, Bhutan|Rife]]\n*[[Ritang, Bhutan|Ritang]]\n*[[Rungzyung]]\n*[[Saidu]]\n*[[Sakteng]]\n*[[Samdrup Choling]]\n*[[Samtengang]]\n*[[Sana, Bhutan|Sana]]\n*[[Samtse]]\n*[[Sangkari]]\n*[[Sarpang]]\n*[[Sasoka]]\n*[[Sassi, Bhutan|Sassi]]\n*[[Sawang, Bhutan|Sawang]]\n*[[Sawaphu]]\n*[[Sengor]]\n*[[Shabling]]\n*[[Shali, Bhutan|Shali]]\n*[[Shamgong Dzong]]\n*[[Shapang]]\n*[[Sharithang]]\n*[[Shingbe]]\n*[[Shingkarap]]\n*[[Shinka, Bhutan|Shinka]]\n*[[Shiuji]]\n*[[Shodug]]\n*[[Shongar Dzong]]\n*[[Shuri, Bhutan|Shuri]]\n*[[Singye Dzong]]\n*[[Suchha]]\n*[[Sufali]]\n*[[Sunphan]]\n*[[Tala, Bhutan|Tala]]\n*[[Tamji]]\n*[[Tangsebi]]\n*[[Taripe]]\n*[[Tashichho Dzong]]\n*[[Tashtanje]]\n*[[Tendu, Bhutan|Tendu]]\n*[[Thebong]]\n*[[Thimphu]]\n*[[Thode]]\n*[[Thrimshing]]\n*[[Thumgaon]]\n*[[Thunkar]]\n*[[Tima, Bhutan|Tima]]\n*[[Tobrang]]\n*[[Tongla Kenga]]\n*[[Tormoshangsa]]\n*[[Tosumani]]\n*[[Trashigang]]\n*[[Trashiyangtse]]\n*[[Trongsa Dzong]]\n*[[Tsangka]]\n*[[Tshalunang]]\n*[[Tse Kang]]\n*[[Tungka La]]\n*[[Ura, Bhutan|Ura]]\n*[[Usak, Bhutan|Usak]]\n*[[Wangchukling]]\n*[[Wangdue Phodrang]]\n*[[Yalang]]\n*[[Yuwak]]\n{{Div col end}}\n\n==Notes and references==\n<references />\n\n==External links==\n{{Div col|small=yes}}\n*{{cite web|url=http://www.election-bhutan.org.bt/2011/finaldelimitation/bumthang.pdf |format=PDF |title=Chiwogs in Bumthang |publisher=[[Elections in Bhutan|Election Commission]] of [[Government of Bhutan|Bhutan]] |year=2011 |accessdate=2011-07-28 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web